<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DEVSHOP 로그인</title>
    <style>
        /* ... (이전의 구조적 스타일 유지) ... */
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8f8f8; }
        .header-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; }
        .right-menu a { margin-left: 10px; text-decoration: none; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 400px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .input-group { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .input-group input { width: 100%; padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .btn-login { width: 100%; padding: 10px; background-color: #ccc; border: none; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; }
        .links a { margin: 0 5px; text-decoration: none; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
        .social-login button { width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background-color: #fff; cursor: pointer; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="header-top">
    <div class="logo">DEVSHOP</div>
    <div class="right-menu">
        <a href="#">고객센터</a>
        <a href="#">마이페이지</a>
        <a href="/">로그인</a>
        <span class="menu-icon">☰</span>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <h2 class="logo" style="text-align: center;">DEVSHOP</h2>

    <form action="/users/login">
        <div class="input-group">
            <input type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="이메일 주소 (예: sample@dev.com)">
        </div>

        <div class="input-group">
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호">
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn-login">로그인</button>
    </form>

    <div class="links" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
        <a href="/join">이메일 가입</a> |
        <a href="/findEmail">이메일 찾기</a> |
        <a href="/findPassword">비밀번호 찾기</a>
    </div>

    <div class="social-login" style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <button style="background-color: #03c75a; color: white;">N 네이버 로그인</button>
        <button style="background-color: #fee500; color: black;">K 카카오 로그인</button>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#">회사소개</a> |
        <a href="#">이용약관</a> |
        <a href="#">개인정보처리방침</a> |
        <a href="#">사업자정보확인</a>
    </div>
    <p>Created By HR | All Right Reserved</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>